article.description: Jake Toolson had 21 points as Utah Valley beat Cal State Northridge 92-84 in the first round of the College Basketball Invitational on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Toolson lifts Utah Valley over CS Northridge 92-84 in CBI
article.linkText: Toolson lifts Utah Valley over CS Northridge 92-84 in CBI
article.story: OREM, Utah -- Jake Toolson had 21 points as Utah Valley beat Cal State Northridge 92-84 in the first round of the College Basketball Invitational on Tuesday night. Baylee Steele had 19 points for Utah Valley (25-9). Richard Harward added 15 points. Isaiah White had 15 points for the hosts. Lamine Diane had 27 points for the Matadors (13-21). Terrell Gomez added 22 points. Elijah Harkless had 13 points. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
